        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500/10 to-orange-500/10 p-5 rounded-lg border border-yellow-500/20">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400">Ecombox.vn - International Awards & Recognition (2025)</h3>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-muted">
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Award / Program</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 font-semibold">Title / Result</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 font-semibold">Strategic Significance</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-muted-foreground">
                  <tr class="border-b border-muted/50">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Startup Wheel 2025</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground">Champion (Vietnam Youth Startup)</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Certified as the top startup in Young Enterprise segment, opening access to major investment funds.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-muted/50">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Global EntrePrep Incubator 2025 (GE25)</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground">Top Startup</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Selected for global incubation program with access to up to $2M funding from VinVentures, Quest Ventures.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-muted/50">
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Tuoi Tre Startup Award 2025</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground">Outstanding Figure</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Enhanced brand recognition and credibility in mainstream media.</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4">Shopee Open Platform</td>
                    <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-foreground">Official Partner</td>
                    <td class="py-3">Certified technical capability and reliability, ensuring uninterrupted operations.</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/5 p-5 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-start">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">2nd Runner-up of Data Analysis at Heading for the Future Vietnam</h3>
              <p class="text-primary font-medium whitespace-nowrap ml-2">July 2024</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 text-muted-foreground">
              <li>Proficient in analyzing market research and targeting customers</li>
              <li>Managed sales activities, operations, and enhanced enterprise platform development solutions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/5 p-5 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-start">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Top 5 of Heineken Hackathon (E-commerce field at Heading for the Future Vietnam)</h3>
              <p class="text-primary font-medium whitespace-nowrap ml-2">July 2024</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/5 p-5 rounded-lg">
